{
  "stem": "9701.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, I don't know where the goddamn bitch is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if I find her, and if she's still alive, I will kill her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And with that, I just took off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on my way I had to pass the Jewish hardware store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The two display windows were broken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were people milling around, laughing and joking, and reaching into the store and taking stuff out which I also did not understand.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I approached my aunt's house, I could see my mother and my aunt looking out the window.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wondered, you know, what are they looking at?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They surely don't want to see what I just saw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother opened the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she looked kind of grotesque.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was quite a bit taller and thinner than my aunt Kaethe, that's K-A-E-T-H-E.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was wearing my aunt's clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We exchanged what happened to each other since we'd last seen each other a couple hours earlier that day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother said that about 10 minutes after I left for school, some Nazis came to the house and they arrested my father.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was still in his pajamas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They did not give him permission to get dressed or even to put a coat on on this very cold day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as he was being walked out the door, he said to my mother, try to find Kaethe and try to stay together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A couple of the Nazis stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they broke the windows in our building and did some other vandalism, broke furniture and dishes and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After they left, my mother closed the shutters and secured the building, ran down the street to my aunt's house, not realizing she was still wearing her nightgown.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
